The Partnership for Maternal, Newborn &amp; Child Health was launched in September 2005, representing an unprecedented collaboration of the world's leading maternal, newborn and child health advocates. Around 80 organisations belong to the partnership, including the World Health Organisation (WHO) for example. http://www.who.int/pmnch/en/&#xd;
